# UI Patterns

## Collapsible Sections

All `<details>` elements should use the `section-panel` CSS class. This adds gray top/bottom borders to the `<summary>`, making it visually distinct and obviously clickable.

```erb
<details class="section-panel">
  <summary>Section Title</summary>
  ...content...
</details>
```

Do not use `<hr>` tags to visually separate `<details>` elements -- the `section-panel` borders handle this.
